---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cookie policy" description="Cookie policy of Resolve IT — which cookies we use and why.">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Cookie policy</h1>
      <p>Which cookies we use and why.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <p class="text-muted"><em>Last updated: June 2026.</em></p>

      <h2>1. What are cookies?</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit our website. They help the website function correctly and allow us to analyse usage.</p>

      <h2>2. Which cookies do we use?</h2>
      <h3>Functional cookies</h3>
      <p>These are necessary for the website to function and cannot be disabled.</p>

      <h3>Analytical cookies</h3>
      <p>With your consent, we use analytical cookies to understand how visitors use the website, so we can improve it.</p>

      <h2>3. Managing consent</h2>
      <p>On your first visit we ask for consent to place non-essential cookies. You can adjust your preferences at any time via the cookie settings or by deleting cookies in your browser.</p>

      <h2>4. Deleting cookies</h2>
      <p>You can delete cookies via your browser settings. Please note that certain website features may then no longer work properly.</p>

      <h2>5. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about our cookie policy? Get in touch at <a href="mailto:contact@resolveit.nl">contact@resolveit.nl</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
</content>
